142
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:29,620
Kita akan bertemu di kamp militer malam ini.

143
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:30,160
Saudara laki-laki.

144
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,500
Surat dari Nanjing.

145
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:47,750
Dia benar-benar pantas menyandang gelar
Komandan Nanjing.

146
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:48,870
Sangat cepat.

147
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,360
Mereka sudah menemukan

148
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,200
