152
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:01,870
Bensheng,

153
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,720
Anda harus menerimanya dengan benar.

154
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,980
Begitu mereka tiba,

155
