174
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:41,460
Aku bermaksud baik, Saudaraku!

175
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:44,200
Anda pergi ke sana hari ini.

176
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,330
Bengkel tinta itu mungkin telah terbongkar.

177
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:48,670
